# chercher-plugin-txt

[Chercher](https://github.com/dnlzrgz/chercher) plugin that adds support for plain text files.

## Installation

```bash
uv tool install --with chercher-plugin-txt chercher
```

## Settings

> [!NOTE]
> This plugin does not requires any additional settings.
